{"lastModified":1770205784363,"uri":"c::8344947358::vessel::d5cbfc37-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\n‘Lady Rina' (Ex Andrea) is a luxurious yacht designed by the famous architect Stefano Righini, built by the well respected Italian shipyard Baglietto in 1987 and refitted to the highest standards in 2018/2019 and 2022. As prestigious and long the history of Baglietto is, ‘Lady Rina’ is also a piece of that history on its own as a milestone in the production of luxury megayachts with the creation of two sisterships stepping into the era of the fast aluminum hulls, the Lady Anfimar and Adler. This reflected elegantly with her maiden owners Swarowski. ‘Lady Rina' has been cherished and maintained by her previous owners and withstood time well to stand proudly amongst her newer counterparts. The new owners gave her the tender loving care that she deserved to\nbring her to today‘s standards, both on safety and aesthetically, with special attention to the finesse that Stefano Righini and Baglietto gave her. She presents a nice layout of six spacious cabins, all with en-suite facilities - two double cabins (one convertible to two single beds), two twin cabins with one pullman berth each and two single cabins with one pullman berth each. Her professional crew of six will guarantee an unforgettable cruising experience.","blueprint":{"name":"LADY RINA","images":["/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cbfc37-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::54d20600-a042-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cbfc37-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5571c870-a042-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cbfc37-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::56240170-a042-11ee-9209-29ad3ed1d3b4.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cbfc37-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5705aee0-a042-11ee-9209-29ad